      <title>沃尔沃汽车因中国电动汽车关税不确定性调整销售预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/volvo-car-profit-jumps-on-firm-prices-ev-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于欧盟与中国在支持电动汽车行业问题上产生的贸易冲突可能对其产生影响，沃尔沃汽车公司略微下调了今年的汽车销量预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/volvo-car-profit-jumps-on-firm-prices-ev-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
